    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can use the <code>flatCollect()</code> pattern from <a href=\"http://www.eclipse.org/collections/\">Eclipse Collections</a>.</p>\n\n<pre><code>MutableList&lt;List&lt;Object&gt;&gt; list = Lists.mutable.empty();\nMutableList&lt;Object&gt; flat = list.flatCollect(each -&gt; each);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>If you can't change list from <code>List</code>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>List&lt;List&lt;Object&gt;&gt; list = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();\nList&lt;Object&gt; flat = ListAdapter.adapt(list).flatCollect(each -&gt; each);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Note: I am a contributor to Eclipse Collections.</p>\n"
  }, {
