    "body" : "<p><code>flatmap</code> is better but there are other ways to achieve the same</p>\n\n<pre><code>List&lt;List&lt;Object&gt;&gt; listOfList = ... // fill\n\nList&lt;Object&gt; collect = \n      listOfList.stream()\n                .collect(ArrayList::new, List::addAll, List::addAll);\n</code></pre>\n"
